    </div>
    <div class="card col-sm-6">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 mx-auto">
            <%= image_tag "home_renter.png"%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h5 class="card-title">Are you a Rentee?</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Travel without carrying all of your surf gear and choose onde of our parterns Premium surfboardsand at fair rates! Regardless of your surfing level, preferred type of surfboard or budget, we have a board to help you boost your surfing experience. </p>
